Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.95,0:00:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.85,0:00:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.56,0:00:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.47,0:00:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.24,0:00:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.15,0:00:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.79,0:00:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.16,0:00:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.26,0:01:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.83,0:01:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.31,0:01:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.01,0:01:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.45,0:01:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.92,0:01:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我從頭開始翻譯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.71,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興,非常高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.78,0:01:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開心得滿心飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.21,0:01:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興,非常高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開心得滿心飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.02,0:02:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑不住的喜悅\N在我的心裡飛舞著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.03,0:02:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.70,0:02:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.66,0:02:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.97,0:02:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領家教費的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是…是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.05,0:02:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥好奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.95,0:02:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下禮拜再麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,下禮拜見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,她忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我忘了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.67,0:03:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次響子忘了帶走的\N能不能請你幫我還給她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.02,0:03:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好,我是御龜壽司店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少錢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4300圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,4300圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我特地擬定的計劃泡湯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.62,0:04:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家教費\N媽媽忘了給你家教費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,家教費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家教費…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.34,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#14 太好了五代!和響子首次約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間過得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.38,0:05:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來到這裡已經一年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了好多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正比較有改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有五代考上大學這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.90,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然內涵還是沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.01,0:05:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝作若無其事,裝作若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一付若無其事的態度…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她…她睡著了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是來偷吃她豆腐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我怎麼睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.72,0:07:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道\N反正我也沒有睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他看到我的糗樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚妳有空嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.86,0:07:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起出去吃頓飯,好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天領到打工錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.90,0:07:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無法請妳\N吃什麼豪華大餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過當然是我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0K…是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,六點鐘碰頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點是“MA.MAISON”\N妳知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,六點MA.MAISON見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.01,0:08:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,六點豆藏見\N(“豆藏”音近“MA.MAISON”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.35,0:08:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了,太棒了,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽見了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.29,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來他記得我來這裡\N今天剛好滿一年啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.32,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟響子約會了\N要穿什麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.16,0:08:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都還沒說耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.04,0:08:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正不是今晚要喝酒\N就是要瘋一瘋,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真驚人,你猜對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我已經有約了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.45,0:09:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要給管理員開個派對\N慶祝她就任一週年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真無情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以囉,大家要喝個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反應怎麼這麼冷淡?妳不方便嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.41,0:09:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我已經有約了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳是主角耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.68,0:09:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微來露個臉?\N六點鐘在豆藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,豆藏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.59,0:09:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他約六點鐘的時候\N在豆藏碰頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,不說就算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正到了六點就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要舉辦宴會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.74,0:10:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你耳朵真好啊\N原來你不只是牙齒會發光而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是愛說笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.94,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要開個派對\N慶祝她就任滿一週年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.98,0:10:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?我不是房客耶\N這不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.75,0:10:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是會費制的,所以要交錢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會偏偏選在同一家店呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.24,0:10:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代如果機靈一點\N選別的地方就好了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要穿哪一件衣服去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.75,0:10:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(MA.MAISON)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像來得太早了,也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘量喝,喝個痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.22,0:11:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,主角請坐在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧,來吧\N管理員先乾一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.83,0:11:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我等一下還有約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.24,0:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經超過六點了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.11,0:11:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,五代怎麼沒來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.25,0:11:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一刻館的人\N全部都會來,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.35,0:11:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子最近忙著交女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去幽會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十分了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,反正女生常常遲到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐著性子等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.12,0:12:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,我又賺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.10,0:12:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩子\N好像是五代的女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到七點,如果她還沒來的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續等到八點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.96,0:13:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在等的人到底是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就乾脆老實招出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經七點了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.47,0:13:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個爛傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然放妳鴿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過份了,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們約在小酒館見面啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.29,0:13:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該是約在MA.MAISON吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是車站附近的咖啡店啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼聽來還真的蠻像的\NMA.MAISON和豆藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.27,0:13:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MA.MAISON,豆藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得快點趕去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經七點多了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能抬去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.05,0:14:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.72,0:14:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以去,我不讓你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也拜託一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經等了一個多小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是被甩了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在生氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐,我要忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我實在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.52,0:15:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼穿成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你還在這裡幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在車站前面柏青哥店\N隔壁的咖啡店裡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.97,0:15:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是響子搞錯地方了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.48,0:15:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是五代那裡的管理員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.09,0:15:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你是五代的朋友…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.82,0:15:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問,你有沒有看到五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.66,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代今天好像去約會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.47,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個女生\N好像叫小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟小津江?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.44,0:16:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊\N二話不說馬上就衝過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.74,0:16:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他結婚以後\N一定會被老婆管得死死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟小津江…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟小津江約會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.55,0:16:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微晚點來\N他居然馬上掉頭去找別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,要不要跟我一起去喝酒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再喝一家,再喝一家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,我陪你喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.05,0:16:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不跟五代講話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,四個人,有位子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.27,0:17:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這家店很便宜\N烤飯糰好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要點那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四位請裡面坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次來這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…小津江?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.05,0:17:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳今天不是跟五代在一起嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪…阪本,你剛才說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.39,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徹底掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.63,0:17:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,難道他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.38,0:19:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位客人好像怪怪的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經打烊了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.53,0:19:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請拿去擦一擦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.23,0:20:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一年前\N我們第一次見面時妳穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.00,0:20:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你一直等我等到現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.18,0:20:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要哭了,我沒有生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.82,0:20:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是讓你等了三個小時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.15,0:20:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦,我真的不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.89,0:20:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微靠過來一點好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.13,0:21:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.07,0:21:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了,在這種氣氛下\N我只要很自然地摟著她就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.34,0:21:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法\N我遲到了那麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.48,0:21:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N原來妳在豆藏等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道\N該怎麼向你道歉才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.88,0:22:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼棒的氣氛\N今年大概不可能會再有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.42,0:22:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我要儘可能地\N儘可能地繞遠路…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳忘了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.87,0:22:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.93,0:22:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看妳突然衝出去\N我們很擔心就趕過來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像沒有必要來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.77,0:22:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,管理員會淋溼的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.31,0:22:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傘給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.28,0:22:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我一起撐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.62,0:22:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.86,0:22:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.73,0:22:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.73,0:22:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.07,0:22:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.37,0:22:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,明天見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.67,0:22:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,今天真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.28,0:22:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.41,0:22:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會淋溼的,快進來躲雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.28,0:22:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.32,0:22:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.65,0:23:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了,我沒有在生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.06,0:23:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.56,0:23:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.40,0:23:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很自然地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想趁這個機會吃我豆腐\N你實在太低級了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.74,0:23:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她居然不會被氣氛給陶醉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.28,0:23:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣得牙癢癢的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.19,0:23:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.15,0:23:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.82,0:23:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不想變成他那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.47,0:23:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代在大學校慶的時候\N聽說要表演人偶劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.64,0:23:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家要一起去看他表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.57,0:23:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.27,0:24:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「危險的兩人人偶劇!\N我已經不行了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.81,0:24:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會,我不會演人偶劇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.05,0:24:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,救命啊,王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.83,0:24:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.25,0:24:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.32,0:24:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.22,0:24:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.56,0:24:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.10,0:25:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.51,0:25:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.02,0:25:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是痛苦的折磨
